@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Home Page";
}

<div class="jumbotron">
    <h2>Sustaining urban communities through an efficient transport model</h2>
    <p class="lead">
        The new travel cards will aim to reduce urban traffic with the use of the public transport model.
        This will significantly reduce CO2 emissions caused by vehicles. It will also prompt those who stay within a 5km
        radius of their work/school location to either walk or cycle. This discourages the use of unnecessary private transportation
        which contributes to high CO2 emissions.
    </p>
    <button type="button" onclick="location.href='@Url.Action("DataInput","Home")'">Proceed</button>
    <br />
    <br />
    <img src="~/myFiles/u19182504(class diagram).png" />
</div>

